title: There Was An Envelope Mixup At The 1964 Oscars, And Sammy Davis Jr Handled It Like A Champ
text: Blacklist domain 'WAIT TIL THE NAACP HEARS ABOUT THIS' There Was An Envelope Mixup At The 1964 Oscars, And Sammy Davis Jr Handled It Like A Champ 5 diggs Oscars 2017 Video The stakes were lower when Sammy Davis Jr. got handed the wrong envelope (the winner he announced first *did* win an Oscar â€” just not the one he was announcing). But he handled it with aplomb. The mixup happens midway through the video, but watch the beginning for Davis Jr.'s excellent impressions.
